{"tid":1675220,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"好攰 屋企人唔支持呢場運動","createTime":"2019-10-25T17:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T03:13:48.000Z","uid":92376,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"beda4db4107560211b4d51cab6d1d6a2343c8429","tid":1675220,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟最近三個月開始接觸攀石呢種運動<br />\n<br />\n叫做爬得唔錯 諗緊有一日可以試下參加搶包山 呢個係我夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過攀石難免會有啲碰傷撞傷咁樣<br />\n所以屋企人都好唔支持我繼續玩呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚我有一日會出事<br />\n仲因為咁 試過好幾次食飯果陣嗌晒大交<br />\n有你無我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得好撚攰<br />\n我只係做運動 點解佢地要唔支持<br />\n巴打們 我應該點做好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://outdoorgearlab-mvnab3pwrvp3t0.stackpathdns.com/photos/15/81/279616_31645_L2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Foutdoorgearlab-mvnab3pwrvp3t0.stackpathdns.com%2Fphotos%2F15%2F81%2F279616_31645_L2.jpg&h=9dcf1d25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c3aaf03db3b7382bb1e3b511394611bb650b58d","tid":1675220,"uid":206337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:08:31.000Z","msg":"撚夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfafbab57077b2c08a67817a9ba6526ab4d674f","tid":1675220,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9c3aaf03db3b7382bb1e3b511394611bb650b58d","tid":1675220,"uid":206337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:08:31.000Z","msg":"撚夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"你想話我屋企人撚我 唔比我追夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910561ab01216088c300034d07c56909837f2183","tid":1675220,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:18:56.000Z","msg":"我支持你 爬多啲<br />\n快手跌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7bf3bc94f3144c5f1ee6acd45c6e9f102bc884","tid":1675220,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUPo8oT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUPo8oT.gif&h=0b30e983&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5983579c63e4087053d4d80fbf270a61f1513dd6","tid":1675220,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"910561ab01216088c300034d07c56909837f2183","tid":1675220,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:18:56.000Z","msg":"我支持你 爬多啲<br />\n快手跌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"係都你死先啦咁撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f38ec80f5051527f48c27835aa23c0931ee08cc","tid":1675220,"uid":98022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:25:10.000Z","msg":"想做就做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21dc07b67b246e22ed97075416ee58a5737f014","tid":1675220,"uid":87890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:43:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3bd82e97606c9aff3781f79c80a80803e4d3471","tid":1675220,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5983579c63e4087053d4d80fbf270a61f1513dd6","tid":1675220,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"910561ab01216088c300034d07c56909837f2183","tid":1675220,"uid":94828,